# Common Layout Widgets

## Container

Adds padding, margins, borders, background color. Single `child` (can be Row/Column).

## GridView

Two-dimensional list with auto-scroll. Use `GridView.count` (columns) or `GridView.extent` (max tile width).

## ListView

Column-like with auto-scroll. Use for lists of items.

## Stack

Overlap widgets; first child is base, rest overlay. Use `Positioned` for placement. Content can't scroll.

## Card

Material card with rounded corners and shadow. Use `SizedBox` to constrain — default size is 0×0.

## ListTile

Specialized row: up to 3 lines of text, optional leading/trailing icons. Often used in Card or ListView.
